They are effective at long range using single shots, but can also burst fire to suppress enemies or inflict heavy close-quarters damage. This makes them reliable weapons that do not excel at any particular role. Due to the use of the same type of ammunition as the precision rifle (G3 SG/1) the German G3 AX battle rifle is able to inflict more damage to the enemies than the other available assault rifles, but it is however somewhat harder to handle.
